1. yum install ansible --> This will install ansible in the system. If it gives message like "Error:Nothing to do", then run below
2. yum install epel-release --> epel is extra packages for enterprise linux,it's the community software repository maintained by people                                   those who use CentOS.It's the alternative of RedHat formal repositories.
3. yum install ansible --> run it again after running the 2nd command.
